<div xmlns:perseus="http://www.perseus.org/meta/perseus.rdfs#" xmlns:dctype="http://purl.org/dc/dcmitype/" xmlns:tufts="http://www.tufts.edu/" xmlns:alph="http://alpheios.net/namespaces/tei" class="alpheios-lex-text_container en">
    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n4937" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλέω</span></b> , <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλέει</span> and <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλεῖ</span>, etc.,
          inf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλήμεναι</span>, part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλεῦντες</span>, ipf. (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐ</span>)<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κάλει</span>, iter. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλέεσκον</span>, aor. (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐ</span>)<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κάλεσσα</span>, part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλἕσ̓σᾶς</span>, pass. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλέονται</span>, ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλεῦντο</span>,
          iter. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλέσκετο</span>, perf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κέκλημαι</span>, plup. 3 pl. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεκλήατο</span>, fut. perf. 2 sing. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεκλήσῃ</span>, mid. aor. (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐ</span>)<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καλέσσατο, καλέσαντο</span>:
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">call</span> by name, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">call</span> together,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">summon, invite</span>, mid., to or for oneself; w. cognate
          acc., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινὰ ἐπώνυμον</span> or <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπίκλησιν καλεῖν</span>, call a person ‘by a name,’
            <i><span class="en">Il. 9.562</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 18.487</span></i>; freq. pass., esp. perf., ‘be called,’ ‘pass
          for,’ often only a poetic amplification of <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">εἶναι, αἲ γὰρ ἐμοὶ τοιόσδε πόσις κεκλημένος εἴη</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 6.244</span></i>; often of inviting to dinner,
          see <i><span class="en">Od. 11.185</span></i>-187; mid., <i><span class="en">Il. 24.193</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            21.380</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
